கெஞ்ச. கும்பிடப்போனதெய்வங்குறுக்கேவந்ததுபோல் நீவந் தாய். i met you  
as if i had met the god whom i was going to worship. கும்பிடப்போனவன்தலையிலேகோயிலிடிந்துவிழுந்தா ற்போல. as if the temple had fallen on the head of him who repaired to it for wor ship; said of occurrences quite opposite to expectation